title: Google\Cloud\DataLabeling\V1beta1\Evaluation
name: Evaluation
description:
Describes an evaluation between a machine learning model's predictions and ground truth labels. Created when an [EvaluationJob][google.cloud.datalabeling.v1beta1.EvaluationJob] runs successfully.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.datalabeling.v1beta1.Evaluation

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: Output only. Resource name of an evaluation. The name has the following format: "projects/{project_id}/datasets/{dataset_id}/evaluations/{evaluation_id}'

params.name: data.config
params.description: Output only. Options used in the evaluation job that created this evaluation.

params.name: data.evaluation_job_run_time
params.description: Output only. Timestamp for when the evaluation job that created this evaluation ran.

params.name: data.create_time
params.description: Output only. Timestamp for when this evaluation was created.

params.name: data.evaluation_metrics
params.description: Output only. Metrics comparing predictions to ground truth labels.

params.name: data.annotation_type
params.description: Output only. Type of task that the model version being evaluated performs, as defined in the [evaluationJobConfig.inputConfig.annotationType][google.cloud.datalabeling.v1beta1.EvaluationJobConfig.input_config] field of the evaluation job that created this evaluation.

params.name: data.evaluated_item_count
params.description: Output only. The number of items in the ground truth dataset that were used for this evaluation. Only populated when the evaulation is for certain AnnotationTypes.
